d feminist because I am human. I am messy. I’m not trying to be an example. I am not trying to be perfect. I am not trying to say that I have all the answers. I am not trying to say that I’m right. I am just trying--trying to support what I believe in, trying to do some good in this world…” (Gay, x-xi). © 2019, Institute of Advanced Scientific Research, Inc.. All rights reserved.
